{"tid":196340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"賺翻了！他花114萬買坦克 竟在油箱內發現價值7600萬金條","createTime":"2017-04-11T08:41:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T17:00:19.000Z","uid":53379,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f6fa6c1641951c7971a0289bfbcd51595713e4d4","tid":196340,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T08:41:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">賺翻了！他花114萬買坦克 竟在油箱內發現價值7600萬金條</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d17ixjpazu3j94.cloudfront.net/images/2017/04/10/14918092649128n9jwKXm4Kb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd17ixjpazu3j94.cloudfront.net%2Fimages%2F2017%2F04%2F10%2F14918092649128n9jwKXm4Kb.jpg&h=9d391a51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲（圖/翻攝自每日郵報）<br />\n<br />\n買坦克送金條？怎麼會有這麼好康的事！英國一名55歲的軍事迷米德（Nick Mead），砸了約114萬台幣在拍賣網站購入一輛俄國製T54 / 69坦克，到貨時米德與朋友歡天喜地檢視收藏，居然在油箱裡面發現5塊金光閃閃的金條，每個重達5.4公斤，約7600多萬台幣，價值連城。<br />\n<br />\n根據《太陽報》報導，米德是個瘋狂的軍事迷，收藏品眾多，先前還買過陸軍用貨車和阿伯特自走槍，近日花費約114萬元新台幣，在拍賣網站購入一輛俄國的T54/69坦克，因為米德擔心坦克可能裝有未爆彈，請來機械師伯倫（Todd Chamberlain）一起檢查坦克，結果居然在油箱裡發現約5個各為5.45公斤的金條，但拾金不昧的兩人經討論後，將金條交給警方處理，米德也豁達表示，「就算拿不回金條，我還有美麗的坦克。」而警方登記並且調查之後，已將金條還給他們。<br />\n<br />\n▼超幸運的米德花百萬買舊坦克，卻在油箱發現千萬黃金。（圖/翻攝自每日郵報）<br />\n<img src=\"https://ebcnews.s3.amazonaws.com/images/2017/04/10/14918094188526X8Lu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Febcnews.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fimages%2F2017%2F04%2F10%2F14918094188526X8Lu.jpg&h=e57bfaed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據了解，米德已將這些金條存進保險箱中，根據兩人的推測，這些金條應該是1990年波斯灣戰爭期間，有伊拉克士兵趁機掠奪財物，洗劫大量黃金，偷偷放進坦克油箱後，在不知情的狀況下被運回英國，最後輾轉來到米德的手上。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.news.ebc.net.tw/news.php?nid=58749&amp;utm_referrer=android-app%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.news.ebc.net.tw%2Fnews.php%3Fnid%3D58749%26utm_referrer%3Dandroid-app%253A%252F%252Fm.facebook.com&d=LgTIxyFtuo0acoW68XVTBcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=b36a5adc\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.news.ebc.net.tw/news.php?nid=58749&amp;utm_referrer=android-app%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com</a>"},{"pid":"c5b179779c3bc23e3aa2bbc95c8e664c741d2a12","tid":196340,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T09:20:32.000Z","msg":"T-54? 邊到似坦克呀睇過 <br />\nFV433 Abbot就Abbot啦, 求其揾張有樣嘅圖就上, Daily Fail不意外"},{"pid":"14fa2613e12761e76ff21dd9cc79a6db77cbb67c","tid":196340,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T09:22:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>T-54? 邊到似坦克呀睇過 <br />\nFV433 Abbot就Abbot啦, 求其揾張有樣嘅圖就上, Daily Fail不意外</blockquote> <br />\n屌自走槍乜撚翻譯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f6c26f63ca925712186bb1937c4eba11794419","tid":196340,"uid":39750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T09:28:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>T-54? 邊到似坦克呀睇過 <br />\nFV433 Abbot就Abbot啦, 求其揾張有樣嘅圖就上, Daily Fail不意外</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.rbth.com/468x312/2x45/1298x865/all/2017/04/10/nick-mead-27737750-b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.rbth.com%2F468x312%2F2x45%2F1298x865%2Fall%2F2017%2F04%2F10%2Fnick-mead-27737750-b.jpg&h=bcd40074&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢架先係係架t54"},{"pid":"741a927acf66aa79b6a2c2de4995c98e3c4cc306","tid":196340,"uid":39750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T09:29:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>T-54? 邊到似坦克呀睇過 <br />\nFV433 Abbot就Abbot啦, 求其揾張有樣嘅圖就上, Daily Fail不意外</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.rbth.com/468x312/2x45/1298x865/all/2017/04/10/nick-mead-27737750-b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.rbth.com%2F468x312%2F2x45%2F1298x865%2Fall%2F2017%2F04%2F10%2Fnick-mead-27737750-b.jpg&h=bcd40074&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢架先係係架t54</blockquote><br />\n咁有錢